column2: Milte Hi Ankhen Dil Hua Deewana
Dil E Nadan Tujhe Hua Kya Hai
Meri Yaad Mein Tum Na Ansoo Bahana
Mohabbat Mein Aise Zamane Bhi Aaye
Ae Mere Dil Kahin Aur Chal
Main Dil Hoon Ek Armaan Bhara
Koi Nahin Mera Is Duniya Mein
Yeh Hawa Yeh Raat Yeh Chandni
Mujhe Dekho Hasrat Ki Tasveer Hoon
Tere Dar Pe Aaya Hoon Fariyad Lekar
Hazaar Haathwale Mandir Ke Dwar Khule
Apni Naqami Se Mujhko Kaam Hai
Aai Jhumti Bahar Laai Dil Ka Qarar
Mere Jeevan Mein Aaya Hai Kaun
Patthar Dil Ho Gaya Duniya Ka
Raat Ne Kya Kya Khwab Dikhaye
Do Din Ki Mohabbat Mein Hamne
Mere Sang Piya (Woh Hai Koi Dekh Lega)
Tim Tim Taron Ke Deep Jale
Pyar Par Bas To Nahin Hai
Sach Bata Tu Mujh Pe Fida
Pyar Par Bas To Nahin Hai
Pyas Kuchh Aur Bhi Bhadka Di
Aaha Rim Jhim Ke Ye Pyare Pyare
Teri Nigahon Mein Teri Hi Bahon Mein
Maine Bhi Husn Ki Nazron Mein

Jab Chhaye Kabhi Sawan Ki Ghata
